comments.body:
Following the sysctl proposal https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/pull/26057 we would need in addition:

``` go
// Sysctl defines a kernel parameter to be set
type Sysctl struct {
    // Name of a property to set
    Name string `json:"name"`
    // Value of a property to set
    Value string `json:"value"`
}

type LinuxPodSandboxConfig struct {
    // Sysctls hold a list of namespaced sysctls used for the pod. They are only allowed
    // if the respective host namespace setting pod.spec.hostIPC or pod.spec.hostNetwork
    // are false.
    Sysctls []Sysctl
}
```

Maybe, alternatively just:

``` go
SysCtls map[string]string
```

